set_property -dict { PACKAGE_PIN V7 IOSTANDARD LVCMOS33 } [get_ports dac_xfer_n]

## XADC channel 1 differential input. EGo1 W1 potentiometer drives AD1P/C12;
## AD1N/B12 is the matching negative input on XC7A35T-1CSG324C.
set_property -dict { PACKAGE_PIN C12 IOSTANDARD LVCMOS33 } [get_ports xadc_vauxp1]
set_property -dict { PACKAGE_PIN B12 IOSTANDARD LVCMOS33 } [get_ports xadc_vauxn1]

## 32-bit expansion header J5. High-Z by default in the design; DIP7 enables test pattern drive.
